Class SavingsAccount

  • java.lang.Object
    • Account
      • SavingsAccount

  • public class SavingsAccount
extends Account
    The following class is a subclass of account, with the unique specification that it must not allow any overdraws. Since the account class already throws an exception when any overdraft attempt is made, we do not need to provide any further implementation. It is inherited.
